<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
  <title>My Media Adventure</title>
</head>

<body>


    <h1>Adhithya's Media Adventure</h1>

    <p>
      Welcome to my media adventure! I enjoy basketball, fishing, and coding,
      and this webpage highlights some of my favorite things.
    </p>

    <hr>

    <h2>Basketball Gallery</h2>

    <p>
      These images show some of my favorite interests and activities.
    </p>

    <img src="basketball.png" alt="A basketball game in action" width="300" height="300">
    <img src="fishing.png" alt="Fishing by the water" width="300" height="300">
    <img src="coding.png" alt="Coding on a computer" width="300" height="300">

    <hr>

    <h2>Music and Basketball Highlights</h2>

    <p>
      One of my favorite songs is <b>Inside Out by Duster</b>. Listen to the music
      and enjoy some basketball highlights from great players.
    </p>

    <audio controls loop>
      <source src="music.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
      Your browser does not support the audio tag.
    </audio>

    <br><br>

    <video width="500" height="350" controls poster="poster.png" loop>
      <source src="basketball_highlights.mp4" type="video/mp4">
      Your browser does not support the video tag.
    </video>

    <hr>

    <h2>Basketball Game Zone</h2>

    <p>
      Play a basketball-themed Scratch game that involves jumping
    </p>

    <iframe
      src="https://scratch.mit.edu/projects/60917032/embed"
      allowtransparency="true"
      width="500"
      height="400"
      frameborder="0"
      scrolling="no"
      allowfullscreen>
    </iframe>

    <hr>

    <h2>About Me</h2>

    <p>
      My name is Adhithya Natarajan. I am 15 years old and live in Oklahoma.
      I enjoy basketball, fishing, and coding. One of my goals is to build my
      own app in the future and continue improving my programming skills.
    </p>

    <hr>

    <h2>Mission Complete!</h2>

    <p>
      I used image, audio, video, and iframe tags to create my personalized
      media adventure webpage.
    </p>

  

</body>

</html>